---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout title="PlantPal — Privacy Policy" description="PlantPal privacy policy. Your plant data stays private.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <a href="/" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white text-sm transition mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
      ← Back to Home
    </a>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">Privacy Policy — PlantPal</h1>
    <p class="text-white/30 mb-10">Last updated: March 12, 2026</p>

    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">PlantPal is a plant care and identification app developed by Justin Bundrick / BunjiSolutions. Your privacy matters. Here's exactly what we do and don't do with your data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data We Collect</h2>
    
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Data Stored On Your Device</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Plant names, species, care schedules, and notes you enter</li>
      <li>Photos you take or import of your plants</li>
      <li>Watering logs, care activity history, and fertilizer records</li>
      <li>App preferences and settings</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">All of this data is stored locally on your device using Apple's SwiftData framework. If you enable iCloud, your data syncs across your Apple devices via Apple's CloudKit — we never see or access your iCloud data.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Plant Identification</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">When you use the plant identification or health diagnosis feature, your plant photo is sent to Plant.id (a third-party service by Kindwise) for analysis. The photo is transmitted securely over HTTPS and is used solely for identification purposes. We do not store your photos on any server. Please review <a href="https://web.plant.id/privacy-policy/" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300 underline">Plant.id's privacy policy</a> for their data handling practices.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Camera and Photo Library</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">PlantPal requests camera access for plant identification and the light meter feature. Photo library access is used for importing plant photos. These permissions are used only for the stated purposes and can be revoked at any time in iOS Settings.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data We Do NOT Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>We do not collect personal information (name, email, phone number)</li>
      <li>We do not track your location</li>
      <li>We do not use analytics or tracking SDKs</li>
      <li>We do not sell or share any data with third parties</li>
      <li>We do not display ads</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Subscriptions</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">PlantPal Pro is available as a monthly or yearly auto-renewable subscription. Payment is processed entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not have access to your payment information. You can manage or cancel subscriptions in your Apple ID settings at any time.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">PlantPal does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. The app does not require account creation or personal information to use.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Questions? Reach out at <a href="mailto:justinbundrick@gmail.com" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300 underline">justinbundrick@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
